                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Autonomy with connection</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Acquired companies retain their brand, culture, client relationships and product vision. A mental health specialist remains a mental health specialist. But via standardised APIs and open standards (FHIR, HL7), all companies are connected.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">02</div>
