                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Complementary selection</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">PCD deliberately selects companies that complement each other: an EHR supplier, a teleconsultation platform, a scheduling solution and a patient portal strengthen each other's value proposition. Together they offer healthcare organisations an integrated proposition that no single company could deliver alone.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">03</div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Shared services</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Compliance (NEN 7510, GDPR), legal affairs, information security and quality management are shared across the ecosystem. This lowers costs and raises compliance levels for all participants.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm">
                    <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Ecosystem &gt; consolidation</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Stronger together, without losing identity.</p>
