                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">PCD's <a href="{{ langPrefix }}/investeerders-partners" class="text-brand-blue hover:text-brand-blue-dark font-medium">investment strategy</a> targets an IRR of >20%. Network effects ensure that the value of the ecosystem grows non-linearly: each new company increases the value of all existing participants through cross-selling and a shared client base.</p>
